{"tid":1653421,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家可以集體投訴apple將數據傳去騰訊","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:00.000Z","uid":58335,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a08cdd80e6c8d6efcd2525a753e5a5c4ab2d4a66","tid":1653421,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"打電話又好/寫email又好<br />\n用得爛果都係想安全有私隱者<br />\n而家竟然將我哋啲個人資料送中？？<br />\n<br />\n中華民國旗冇左少人出聲<br />\n到今日個人資料送中都冇人出聲既話<br />\n聽日你成部機資料送中都得<br />\n咁貴買部機同用支那機有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲投訴佢<br />\n要佢作出交代<br />\n如果連呢啲終極和理非都唔做<br />\n你哋返去早啲訓啦<br />\n以後唔好話抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1951d92f39900cae7905b634d06e2c4ea4831fd","tid":1653421,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e29dc198a69f3505f12f3f4184e6aeb93591dd0","tid":1653421,"uid":235644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689591fa63b47c50419edf339e2dcd4bfd3e2180","tid":1653421,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648bc93e799fc8b462257d9cca6f7fb02494208b","tid":1653421,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset